 />\n個陣我開始留意佢<br />\n但真正熱愛佢就係因為睇到小小蟲嘅MV<br />\n見佢個文青斯文look<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />笑起嚟勁腼腆<br />\n加上首歌又好sweet 不自覺就愛上<br />\n聽完成隻橙月發現首首歌都勁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後先再發掘番佢其他作品嚟聽<br />\n<br />\n我係因為佢先識咩叫R&amp;B<br />\n聽佢現場d R&amp;B即興改編同轉音真係覺得佢係神！<br />\n佢嘅歌只有佢自己先唱得好聽 其他人唱只會唱得亂七八糟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有佢唔係普通「歌手」 佢真係完全以生命做音樂<br />\n識咁多種樂器 又唱又作又編又演奏<br />\n講真全世界真係好難揾到好似佢咁屈機嘅音樂人<br />\n<br />\n其實我諗大部分人都知道佢係音樂才子<br />\n但真係好少人留意到佢/識欣賞佢嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nesp歌手要係香港樂壇生存一定要唱k歌<br />\n覺得好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np.s. 方大同真係樂壇清泉 有才華有氣質 性格謙卑有禮 私生活又檢點<br />\n但偏偏娛樂圈從來唔講實力 係要製造下花邊新聞先會有人留意 先會受歡迎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你睇下吳若希&hellip;&hellip;唉 唔識講"},{"pid":"b880df7b18a03620a84a08e910a6df89de1e07ab","tid":220861,"uid":21905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T17:34:55.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38d951f0ceb33a02edea67c740b79242dc4cd0b","tid":220861,"uid":38934,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T18:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>15開始鍾意佢<br />\n人生第一個演唱會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n十週年個個音樂很窮同西遊記試聽會都有去<br />\n橙月係我最愛個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢彈結他個專注樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我人生睇第一個演場會都俾左15<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係soulboy lights up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成隻15都係左抄右抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><