\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個 mv <br />\n唯美到！首歌聽一萬次都唔厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉完全同意要花邊先有人留意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  佢係一個性格咁好既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又有才。我好希望佢可以大紅大紫"},{"pid":"57ccadae3aa9c9ea7906cfcf62e711ac9c107051","tid":220861,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:00:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意佢頭兩隻碟... 始終覺得r&amp;b 啱 佢, 之後玩 rock 玩alternative 唔覺得好適合佢</blockquote><br />\nR&amp;B 係佢老本行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我都會支持佢試唔同風格既。唔試點知得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fb11bf66333a25f3fb6b6a2f226cf1a2cb6fff","tid":220861,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:04:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抄歌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講下佢邊首歌抄邊首歌?</blockquote><br />\n二人遊同gravity前奏抄到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你係咪玩開音樂既？ 玩左幾耐？<br />\n我咁問只係想知你係咪係有音樂知識基礎下下此定論，定係純粹憑感覺 up. <br />\n我只可以話你話一個音樂人抄人地歌係最大侮辱，請唔好係無基礎下斷言。人言可畏。<br />\n再者，其實音樂本來就有相通點。寫歌時參考其他歌既結構其實十分正常。參考結構又係咪等同抄歌？係既話其實九成歌都唔係原創。"},{"pid":"b34212431e28a7fc5c7ad4ce1fcc80007c7b899f","tid":220861,"uid":69115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:10:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>抄歌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n講下佢邊首歌抄邊首歌?</blockquote><br />\n二人遊同gravity前奏抄到十足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj